TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
If you meant a deaf leopard, that's one of the ingredients.

Waiter, there's a Firefox in my soup!

Is the fox on fire? or would you prefer our Chrome soup?

Waiter, there's and IE6 in my sou...IE6 has stopped working.

That is SO outdated. But, then again, when my computer with Windows XP blew up, that must have been where the files of IE6 went.

Waiter, there's an outdated Windows XP in my soup!

Yup. and we no longer provide support for WinXP soups.

Waiter!!! There's a furry computer mouse in my soup, and it makes squeaky noises! >:-[

KILL IT WITH FIRE!

Waiter! There's an HO scale UP 844 in my soup!

I really don't know what to say.

Waiter, there's a Universe Sandbox 2 in my soup!

Yes, i have bought it. You should too.

Waiter, there's a 4D tesseract in my soup! It is showing signs of non-euclidean geometry!

Quick! Run before it asks for money!

Waiter! There's a Reichtangle in my soup!
Defeat it with the military, because I assume it is trying to make a Fourth Reich out of Germany.

I can only believe that what is in your soup is a piece of the triforce. In that case, find the other 2 diners who have the other pieces in their soup.

Waiter! There's an Omega Ruby stolen from Game Freak in my soup!

Don't worry, once we take them from him, they don't exist anymore.

Waiter! There's an orange in my soup!

Orange you glad it wasn't an old joke?

Waiter! There's soup in my soup!

That's no soup in your soup, silly, it's machine oil :-]

Waiter!!! There's my soup in a fly! >:-[

Ahem... what type of fly are we talking about, sir?

Soup, there's a talk in my waiter!

WELL THEN TAKE IT OUT!!!!

Waiter there's a waiter in my soup.

Waiter you callin' me over for then?

Waiter, there's a Quagmire in my soup.

What the [sAMPLE TEXT] is a quagmire?

Waiter! There's a Bork in my soup!

At least it's not a piece of metal..

Waiter! There's a plate in my soup!

[REDATED]

WAITER! There is a ERROR 404 in my soup!!

ERROR 502: NEW KSP UPDATE

(hehe)

Waiter, there's a 502 Error in my soup!

You got a Bad gateway to Duna!

Waiter there is a error 500 in my soup!

No, that's an error 300.

Waiter, there's a enemy Scout in my soup! He is attempting to steal the intelligence!

Kill it with your fork!

Uh......waiter? There's a [REDACTED] in my soup.

Hm... EW! THAT IS FLIPING DISSGUSTING!

Waiter there is a train in my soup and its called 0.24 hypetrain!

It just happened to crash there. It's like Windows Vista in that regard.

Waiter! There's an introvert in my soup~
